"RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah! Bless Muhammad and the family of Muhammad and defend Your guard, Your ambassador, Your speech who establish Your Justice, who will dignify Your honour. Who will speak on Your behalf, the revealer of Your judgment, Your sight and Your ear, the testimony of Your servant, Your proof on Your creature, the struggle in Your path and the diligent in Your obedience.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ صَلِّ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ وَّاٰلِ مُحَمَّدٍ، وَادْفَعْ عَنْ وَلِيِّكَ وَخَلِيْفَتِكَ وَلِسَانِكَ وَالْقَاۗئِمِ بِقِسْطِكَ، وَالْمُعَظِّمِ لِحُرْمَتِكَ، وَالْمُعَبِّرِ عَنْكَ، وَالنَّاطِقِ بِحُكْمِكَ، وَعَيْنِكَ النَّاظِرَةِ، وَاُذُنِكَ السَّامِعَةِ، وَشَاهِدِ عِبَادِكَ، وَحُجَّتِكَ عَلٰى خَلْقِكَ، وَالْمُجَاهِدِ فِيْ سَبِيْلِكَ، وَالْمُجْتَهِدِ فِيْ طَاعَتِكَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "